"restore\"`** — This conflicts with the common `dotnet restore` command. Not technically invalid but a very bad idea.","outputTokens":593},"id":"7c1e07e5-9586-4d09-9f35-ab6d22063e46","timestamp":"2026-04-04T00:37:04.308Z","parentId":"44b521f7-3d59-4a5c-9575-7c3d080971d4"}
